findings.recommendation:
Fix the root reentrancy issue (CEI pattern). Also consider adding an invariant check:

require(address(this).balance >= totalDeposits, "Invariant violated");

Or track accounting separately from ETH balance to detect discrepancies.

Remove the receive() fallback or make it a plain ether receiver without auto-depositing:

receive() external payable {
    // Do not auto-deposit; require explicit deposit() call
    revert("Use deposit() function");
}

Or keep it but ensure it doesn't create accounting inconsistencies.

